---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { nowUpdates } from "../data/now";
---

<BaseLayout title="Now | jhle0" description="What I am up to now">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">Right now</p>
    <h1>NOW</h1>
    <p class="intro-copy">
      최근에 무엇을 공부하고 만들고 있는지, 짧은 타임라인 형태로 남기는 현재
      로그.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-block timeline">
    <ul class="timeline-list">
      {
        nowUpdates.map((item) => (
          <li class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker" />
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <p class="timeline-date">{item.date}</p>
              <p>{item.text}</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
